snippet.title: My Perfume Collection 2021 | Dossier Perfume Review | Baccarat Rouge 540 Dupe | Ambery Saffron
snippet.description:
Check out my latest installment of My Perfume Collection 2021 videos comparing the Dossier Ambery Saffron to the Baccarat Rouge 540! In this Dossier perfume review, I am comparing the scent and all other details of the Dossier Ambery Saffron to the luxury perfume, Baccarat Rouge 540 to see if it a good dupe scent. I also compare this to the Cloud by Ariana Grande to determine which is a better version of the luxury fragrance. 

Dossier is a clean, cruelty free, vegan, fragrance brand that specializes in the fragrances and perfumes inspired by well known, luxury perfumes and fragrances. The Dossier perfumes are high quality, affordable alternatives to the luxury fragrances that we all know and love!
